OL,3,CGuernsey scraps campaign grant for
OL,4,Celection candidates
OL,6,FPoliticians in have voted to scrap the
OL,7,Fcampaign grant given to electoral
OL,8,Fcandidates.
OL,10,FThe funding, worth #500, was intended
OL,11,Fto help with campaign expenses during
OL,12,Fa General Election.
OL,14,FThe Assembly also voted to reduce the
OL,15,Famount political candidates and
OL,16,Fparties can spend when campaigning for
OL,17,Felections.
OL,19,FThe maximum that can be spent by
OL,20,Findividuals is now #6,000 and for
OL,21,Fparties, it is #12,000.
